    <string name="help_text">Movie Time is an easy game to play. 
        You can select the movie categories you want to play with or, if you\'re brave, 
        you can try your hand at any movie in the database. Under the options you can 
        set the difficulty by chosing 3 possible movie title choices (easy), 6 possible 
        choices (medium), or 9 movie titles (hard). You can also choose between limited 
        questions or unlimited questions. In limited mode, you are scored by the percentage 
        of questions you get correct. In unlimited mode, the questions keep coming until 
        you get one wrong.  Your score is based on how many you get right in a row. 
        If you\'re ready, make your selections and show the world how smart you are.</string>
